Title:

The appearance of the "Введіть номер ТТН" inscription in the Admin bot after clicking on the "Назад" button
after changing the order status to "Доставляється" order status

Description:

After clicking the "Назад" button after changing the status of the order to "Доставляється", a response is received
from the system in the form of the inscription "Введіть номер ТТН" in the Admin bot

Expected result:

By clicking on the "Назад" button, a message from the system "Введіть номер ТТН" appears and automatically deleted immediately

Actual result:

A message from the system "Введіть номер ТТН" appears but didn`t automatically deleted


Steps to reproduce:

Create a new order through the Shop bot

The new order that was just created in the previous step will automatically appear in the "QA Admin chanell" bot

Under the new order in the "QA Admin chanell" bot, click on the "Взять в обработку" button - this order will be displayed in the Admin bot

In the Admin bot, click on the "Статус виконання" button and select "Доставляється"

Click on the "Назад" button, simulating changes in the order, in response take a message from the system "Введіть номер ТТН"


Reproducibility:

Always

Severity:

Minor

Priority:

Medium

Workaround:

Only fix the system
